          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", it’s a toll road where enthusiasts go to really see what their vehicle can do. Reports indicate there were two people in the Ferrari when they both noticed smoke. Pulling over, they were able to get out safely before the fire spread to the cabin. Then they were helpless while waiting for firefighters to arrive.",
